data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this lovely single-level condo located in North Knoxville, TN. This 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem is an ideal retreat for those seeking a hassle-free lifestyle. The fenced-in patio offers a private outdoor oasis for relaxation and gatherings. With a warm and inviting atmosphere, this home is perfect for those seeking a blend of comfort and practicality in a sought-after location. Don't miss the chance to make this charming condo your own!
